'''Donna Jackson''' is a woman Addison interviewed as a potential surrogate.

==History==
Donna came in to be interviewed by Addison as a potential surrogate. She viewed surrogacy as a business and said she had a skill set she wanted to put to work for Addison. Addison was put off by how formal and business-like the meeting was.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
Her husband is a Navy pilot stationed on an aircraft carrier.

===Familial===
She and her husband have two kids, aged ten and six.
